  "prompt": "Who sings a song titled \"Home\"?",
  "response": "Several artists have songs titled \"Home.\" Some notable ones include:\n\n1. **Michael Bubl\u00e9** - He released \"Home\" in 2005 on his album \"It's Time.\"\n2. **Phillip Phillips** - Known for his version released in 2012, which became popular after he won \"American Idol.\"\n3. **Chris Daughtry** - \"Home\" is a track from his band Daughtry's self-titled debut album, released in 2006.\n4. **Edward Sharpe & The Magnetic Zeros** - Their song \"Home\" was released in 2009 and has become quite popular in indie circles.\n5. **Blake Shelton** - He covered Michael Bubl\u00e9's \"Home\" in 2008, and it became a hit in the country music genre.\n\nEach of these songs brings a different style and sentiment, reflecting the artists' unique approaches to the concept of \"home.\"",
